{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-resume-tsx","path":"/resume/","result":{"data":{"workData":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"4eef6a4a-1595-550e-bd11-75a053dff7f5","html":"<ul>\n<li>Development of an IoT application for Robotics industry.</p></li>\n<li>In charge of front-end tasks using Vue.js, Apollo client, Tailwind, SASS, Jest, and Enzyme.</p></li>\n<li>Back-end tasks done in Node.js using Express, GraphQL(Apollo server), Keycloak, and Docker.</p></li>\n<li>Both Back-end and Front-end are implemented using TypeScript.</p></li>\n<li>Unit and Integration testing. </p></li>\n<li>Agile environment.</p></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"company":"Device Insight","location":"Munich, Germany","position":"Software Engineer","tags":["TypeScript","Vue.js","Node.js","GraphQL","Jest","Docker"],"startDate":"Sep, 2020","endDate":"Dec, 2031"},"fields":{"slug":"/resume/work/DI/"}}},{"node":{"id":"e3bd2b52-8ab1-5b26-9631-d676993d1f16","html":"<ul>\n<li>Develop value added services for Telecommunication providers.</p></li>\n<li>Implement, optimize, and improve legacy Java and JavaScript code in Typescript.</p></li>\n<li>Unit testing.</p></li>\n<li>Worked in an agile, multicultural team.</p></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"company":"European Computer Telecoms","location":"Munich, Germany","position":"Junior Backend JavaScript Developer","tags":["TypeScript","Backend","SQL","Design patterns"],"startDate":"Feb, 2020","endDate":"Aug, 2020"},"fields":{"slug":"/resume/work/ECT/"}}},{"node":{"id":"b2855238-99e7-5bb3-b8c4-fa4cc41bf8bb","html":"<ul>\n<li>Development of a machine anomaly detection system together with an R&#x26;D team in France.</p></li>\n<li>Build a UI using Angular 2+ to allow the user to interact with the data, train ML models, detect anomalies, and watch machine data in real time.</p></li>\n<li>Build a REST API in Python using Flask to host the data analysis. </P></li>\n<li>Create a service to communicate with a PLC via FTP in to retrieve the operation data from the PLC, and save it in the InfluxDB database. </P></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"company":"Schneider Electric","location":"Ratingen, Germany","position":"Master Thesis Student","tags":["Angular 2+","Node.js","TypeScript","Python","Pandas","Scikit-learn","Flask","Docker","IoT","InfluxDB","MongoDB"],"startDate":"May, 2019","endDate":"Dec, 2019"},"fields":{"slug":"/resume/work/Schneider_thesis/"}}},{"node":{"id":"44b32e3e-a734-588b-890d-a2a53c813d80","html":"<ul>\n<li>Test temperature-monitoring systems for electrical-distribution systems.</p></li>\n<li>Detect anomalies in the electrical distribution systems using Python.</p></li>\n<li>Develop a web application hosted on Azure to interact with the data and get anomalies predictions. </P></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"company":"Schneider Electric","location":"Ratingen, Germany","position":"Intern","tags":["JavaScript","Node.js","jQuery","Bootstrap","Python","Pandas","Scikit-learn","Docker","Azure","IoT"],"startDate":"Sep, 2018","endDate":"Mar, 2019"},"fields":{"slug":"/resume/work/Schneider_internship/"}}},{"node":{"id":"cccad102-95f4-5877-95ff-347376586a41","html":"<ul>\n<li>Design industrial machinery wiring diagrams.</p></li>\n<li>Write technical manuals (english &#x26; spanish) for the manufactured machines.</p></li>\n<li>Program weight indicators and control devices.</p></li>\n<li>Program communications software and value-added tools in Lua, Visual Basic .NET, and SQLite.</p></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"company":"Jorge Jaramillo y Cia","location":"Manizales, Colombia","position":"Field Service Engineer","tags":[" Electrical engineering","Customer relationships","Industrial automation","PLC programming"],"startDate":"May, 2016","endDate":"Sep, 2017"},"fields":{"slug":"/resume/work/JJyCia/"}}},{"node":{"id":"80dd35ae-8bb2-5cef-9f7a-fb929c5018c7","html":"<ul>\n<li>Technical support (mechanical and electrical) for all the packaging lines.</p></li>\n<li>Plan all the maintenance tasks (preventive and corrective) for the production f